{"id":"2548170757","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2548170757","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjU0ODE3MDc1Nw==","status":"current","title":"Tutorial dump de base de staging","version":{"by":{"type":"known","accountId":"612e2e8063f7bb006976b761","accountType":"atlassian","email":"","publicName":"Joaquín Pérez","profilePicture":{"path":"/wiki/aa-avatar/612e2e8063f7bb006976b761","width":48,"height":48,"isDefault":false},"displayName":"Joaquín Pérez","isExternalCollaborator":false,"isGuest":false,"locale":"es","accountStatus":"active","_expandable":{"operations":"","personalSpace":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/user?accountId=612e2e8063f7bb006976b761"}},"when":"2023-03-14T17:43:20.702Z","friendlyWhen":"Mar 14, 2023","message":"","number":1,"minorEdit":false,"syncRev":"5.confluence$content$2548170757.34","syncRevSource":"synchrony-ack","confRev":"confluence$content$2548170757.37","contentTypeModified":false,"_expandable":{"collaborators":"","content":"/rest/api/content/2548170757"},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2548170757/version/1"}},"ancestors":[{"id":"2178416778","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2178416778","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjE3ODQxNjc3OA==","status":"current","title":"Bancard","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":878},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2178416778","tinyui":"/x/igDYgQ","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2178416778","webui":"/spaces/BAN/overview","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2178416778"}},{"id":"2259944189","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2259944189","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjI1OTk0NDE4OQ==","status":"current","title":"Documentación Técnica","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":44304616},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2259944189/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2259944189/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2259944189/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2259944189/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2259944189","tinyui":"/x/-QK0hg","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2259944189","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2259944189/Documentaci+n+T+cnica","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2259944189"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<p>este tutorial est&aacute; pensado para usar el editor mysqlworkbench. para seguir estos pasos lo necesitas tener instalado y ademas configurar la conexi&oacute;n a la/s base/s de dato/s de staging (existe la vieja y la nueva) tal que as&iacute; -&gt;</p><p>para la vieja:</p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"477\" ac:original-width=\"657\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20230314-173716.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p>para la nueva:</p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"472\" ac:original-width=\"663\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20230314-173746.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p>para establecer ambas conexiones utilizaremos el siguiente usuario<strong>: </strong></p><p><strong>u: mooveit</strong></p><p><strong>p: 123mooveit</strong></p><p /><p>una vez tengamos la conexi&oacute;n establecida, seguimos los siguientes pasos:</p><p><strong>para exportar un dump:</strong></p><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>en mysqlworkbench, conectado a la maquina con las bases de staging, vas a las opciones de la barra de arriba y seleccionas <code>Server</code> &gt; <code>Data Export</code></p></li><li><p>&nbsp;ahi te va a salir un listado con todas las bases de la maquina de staging, seleccionas la que queres exportar (por ejemplo <code>commerce_service_production</code> )</p></li><li><p>seleccionas la opci&oacute;n <code>Dump Structure and Data</code></p></li><li><p>abajo del todo, en export options, seleccionas <code>Export to Self-Contained File</code> y le pones el nombre que quieras al archivo .sql que te va a generar con todos los datos y estructura de la base (recomiendo un nombre descriptivo asi luego sabes detectar cual es el archivo)</p></li><li><p>le das a start export y continuar si te lo pide</p></li></ol><p><strong>para import un dump:</strong></p><p>luego para importar la base a tu base local:</p><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>en mysqlworkbench, conectado a la maquina local con tus bases, te vas a <code>Server &gt; Data Import</code></p></li><li><p>en import options, selecciona <code>Import from Self-Contained File</code> apuntando al archivo .sql que acabas de exportar</p></li><li><p>seleccionas la base donde queres importar ese .sql (siguiendo el ejemplo, tu base local que creaste de commerce-service)</p></li><li><p>le das a <code>Start Import</code> </p></li></ol><p /><p>y ah&iacute; ya tendrias importado tu dump de la base de staging en tu base local.</p><p />","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/2548170757"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":622565898},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2548170757/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2548170757/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2548170757/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2548170757/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2548170757","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2548170757/Tutorial+dump+de+base+de+staging","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2548170757","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2548170757","tinyui":"/x/BQDilw","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}